summary: Hi, I'm Israfil Hamidov, an aspiring legal professional, currently pursuing an LLM in International Law at Utrecht University. Through my education and internships, I have gained practical experience in legal drafting, research, and advice. I am an ambitious and friendly individual who enjoys taking on new challenges to grow both personally and professionally. I am seeking opportunities to apply my skills and knowledge in an international organization or law firm in the Netherlands. Please note that I'm eligible for the search-year visa and don't require employer sponsorship.
